r_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8088864?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62","html_url":"https://github.com/hankliu62","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hankliu62/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"open_issues":1,"closed_issues":0,"state":"open","created_at":"2024-03-20T03:36:24Z","updated_at":"2024-03-20T03:37:50Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":null},"comments":0,"created_at":"2024-03-20T03:33:20Z","updated_at":"2024-03-20T03:37:50Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"OWNER","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"React页面卡顿问题通常与组件渲染性能、虚拟DOM的diff算法效率、渲染大量数据时的性能瓶颈有关。以下是一些检测和解决React页面卡顿的方法：\r\n\r\n1. 使用React开发者工具(React DevTools)检查组件渲染行为和性能。\r\n2. 优化组件渲染性能，避免在render方法中进行昂贵的操作，例如深度嵌套的map循环。\r\n3. 使用React.PureComponent或React.memo来避免不必要的重渲染。\r\n4. 对于大型列表和数据表格，考虑使用虚拟滚动(react-virtualized)等技术来提高性能。\r\n5. 使用WebAPI的requestIdleCallback或Performance API来监控渲染性能。\r\n6. 进行代码分割，使用React.lazy和Suspense进行代码分割以提高加载速度和性能。\r\n\r\n示例代码：\r\n``` jsx\r\nimport React, { PureComponent } from 'react';\r\n \r\nclass ExpensiveComponent extends PureComponent {\r\n  render() {\r\n    // 计算密集的render方法\r\n    return (\r\n      <div>\r\n        {this.props.data.map(item => (\r\n          <p key={item.id}>{item.content}</p>\r\n        ))}\r\n      </div>\r\n    );\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n \r\n// 优化后的组件\r\nconst VirtualScroller = React.memo(props => (\r\n  <List height={300} rowHeight={30} rowRenderer={props.rowRenderer} rowsCount={props.rowsCount} />\r\n));\r\n \r\nconst App = () => {\r\n  // 使用React.memo避免不必要的重渲染\r\n  const rowRenderer = ({ index, key, style }) => (\r\n    <div key={key} style={style}>\r\n      Row {index}\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n \r\n  return (\r\n    <div>\r\n      <VirtualScroller rowRenderer={rowRenderer} rowsCount={1000} />\r\n    </div>\r\n  );\r\n};\r\n```\r\n在实际应用中，你可能需要结合使用这些技术和工具，逐步定位和解决卡顿问题。","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/576/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/576/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}